 ) Rd3 { Optically, this looks great for Black since White is totally cramped at the moment, but precision is still needed:} 20. Ba5 Ne4 21. Qf3 Rd6 $1 22. Bxc4 Rf6 $132 { and complications continue. This is probably a good point to stop the analysis for the purposes of this database, although I would encourage you to explore this position even deeper on your own.}  *

